<br>
I won't go too far on this, but I will state the following:<br>
<br>
Without a GM and Guide tool to change/fix alignments, Alignments should not be reinstated.<br>
<br>
Without an INFORMATIVE interface for alignments, they should not be reinstated.<br>
<br>
Without a FV specific version of the LFG tool that takes alignment into account, they should not be reinstated.<br>
<br>
Without a change to how languages work in /chat and /chat tell, the languages should stay how they are.<br>
<br>
Without coding to bring into account faction for alignment, Alignments should not be reinstated.<br>
<br>
There need to be MORE alignment options for EVERY race and more deity options. IF this is the RP server, then we need choices and we need interaction with the GMs.<br>
<br>
Freeform doesn't cut it because, frankly, I have good reason not to trust some of the RPers on this server.<br>
<br>
I will state outright. I waged a war of /petition, /bug, /feedback and email to get the alignment rules revoked and/or changed. If the alignment grouping restriction is returned to the server, it will ruin my fun. If my fun is ruined, you can bet your fun will be ruined. <p><!--EZCODE CENTER START--><div style="text-align:center">Nakath Thunderbush<br>
