I am also well aware that the powers that be dont really give a shit.  What're you going to do?  Going to go play Ultima Online?  They have all of us by the short hairs, and they know it.  Plus, one other thing that most fail to realize is that people treat EQ as a video game and not a roleplaying game. personally, i think that the only way to make FV a true RP environment is to get rid of its special no drop rules.  this is the _only_ chance we have of getting rid of the &quot;fuckos&quot;.  (which is a more accurate term for the &quot;d00ds&quot;).  With the no drop rules changed, the fuckos have no reason to be there, and we can all start rping again.<br>
